---

##  How to Use

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Jenes-Sonkar/javascript-learning.git
```

2. Navigate into the project:

```bash
cd javascript-learning
```

3. Run JavaScript files:

```bash
node filename.js
```

Or open `.html` files in browser for DOM practice.

